\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Dynamical-regime map of the spatially-homogeneous FHN ODE at the median training $\tau = 10.5$. Green: excitable (stable rest state). Orange: oscillatory (limit cycle, tonic firing). Purple: bistable. The black rectangle is the oscillatory training box and the blue rectangle is the excitable training box. It is visually very clear, and supported by a sweep across the full $\tau $ range, that both boxes lie entirely within their respective regimes.\relax }}{4}{figure.caption.3}\protected@file@percent }
