\newlabel{fig:bifurcation}{{1}{4}{Dynamical-regime map of the spatially-homogeneous FHN ODE at the median training $\tau = 10.5$. Green: excitable (stable rest state). Orange: oscillatory (limit cycle, tonic firing). Purple: bistable. The black rectangle is the oscillatory training box and the blue rectangle is the excitable training box. It is visually very clear, and supported by a sweep across the full $\tau $ range, that both boxes lie entirely within their respective regimes.\relax }{figure.caption.3}{}}
\newlabel{fig:bifurcation@cref}{{[figure][1][]1}{[1][3][]4}}
